Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme song playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,DOUBT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[tennis ball thwacking]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I have to admit,\NI was surprised, Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nyou'd ask me to play tennis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,as a way to get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a problem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you first invited me to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,did you know how good I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll be fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but at one time I was actually\Nthe British Junior Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If I ask him if he's British,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,would he think I'm trying\Nto find out more about him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't hurt to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuga, were you raised in the UK?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived in England for about five years\Nwhen I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But save your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing in that story\Nwould reveal L's true identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Well, since it's our first match,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we just play a single set?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-First one to six?\N-[Light] That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a friendly game of tennis.\NNothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself it won't determine\Nif Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know Kira hates to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Fifteen, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Ryuga. You sure don't mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He who strike first, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] What do you mean\Nyou're not at liberty to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're under orders from L\Nnot to discuss the case with anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking for details here,\Njust what you're doing and where.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] You know, Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been more than four months since\Nthis case came to the public's attention
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and they want results.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] People are saying that the NPA\Nis incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That L is incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the department runs away\Nwith their tails between their legs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and we are incompetent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people are left\Nat task force headquarters these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're concerned with public opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then you want to suppress the fact\Nthat most of our detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,would rather a serial killer roam free\Nthen risk their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] What about this L character?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] In my opinion,\Nhe is a lot more capable than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, even as we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,he is risking his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these two really amateurs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think their names are\NLight Yagami and Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the same two guys\Nwho scored perfect on the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Relax, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's true that Kira hates losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also true that most people would\Nrather win than lose. It's human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Is he going to think that I'm Kira\Nif I go for the win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could just lose on purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I do, it could work against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he'd expect Kira to want to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he might also expect me to throw the match\Nto avoid suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I don't see any way that he can\Nprofile me based on a tennis match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I have to assume\Nhe has some other goal in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let him win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuga grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Look at that.\NHe's going for the win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's four games all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] And just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got an umpire and a line judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] You won't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd heard the name\NLight Yagami somewhere before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the '02/'03\NJunior High Tennis Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, during the third year\Naward ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he announced that he was\Nhanging up his racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess he hasn't\Nplayed competitively since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[female student] Hey, hey!\NWhat about my Ryuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you haven't noticed\Nhim holding his own
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,against this former junior high champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I can see the wheels turning,\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] There's no way this tennis match\Nwill deepen our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a token gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An elaborate act to go with\Nso we can say we are closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Because I wanted\Nto play tennis with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll assume I'm preparing\Nto take a step closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,laying the ground work\Nto get to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] And then you're going\Nto try and trap me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,by getting me to say something\Nthat only Kira would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] However, I'm sure you will tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to know\Nif you can trust me first,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course,\Nthe only way to win your trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,will be to share what I know about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] If you want me\Nto discuss Kira with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it would only make sense\Nthat I want to ask for proof
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are in charge\Nof the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And more importantly, that you are\Nreally L, as you've say you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] So, it goes without saying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that the first thing\Nyou're going to want from me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] ...some kind of confirmation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from a third party that you really are L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[both] We'll have to go\Nto task force headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] In all things, one cannot win\Nwith defense alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To win, you must attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Game and set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Won by Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Six games to four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[spectators applauding]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Just as I expected, you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's been a while\Nsince I had to play that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling kind of thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's something\Nthat I wanted to ask you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go somewhere\Nfor a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You humored me with the tennis match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The least I can do,\Nis answer some of your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But before this conversation\Ngoes any further,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that you, Light Yagami,\Nare in fact Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you still wanna ask me something,\Nthan please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] You think I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I say I suspect you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a one percent possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, I don't mind telling you\Nthat once I'm sure you aren't Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can verify\Nthat your deductive skills
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,are as strong as I think they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like nothing more than to have you\Nwork with me on this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One percent, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was well worded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no matter how little he says\Nhe suspects me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it means he has grounds to prevent me\Nfrom meeting anyone on the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It was quite a pre-emptive move\Non his part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This coffee shop is one of my favorites\Nin the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we sit here, there's no chance\Nof anyone overhearing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Thanks for showing me this place.\NI can see why you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,\Nwe're so out of the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no one is gonna give you a hard time\Nabout the way you sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't sit like this because I want to.\NI have to sit like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if I were to sit normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,my deductive skills would immediately\Nbe reduced by roughly 40 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what was it you wanted to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that can wait
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,until you're convinced that I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please, let's talk\Nabout whatever you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under no obligation\Nto do this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,would you mind submitting yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to a test of your\Ndeductive reasoning skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can begin by taking a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Photographs of three notes\Nwritten by prison inmates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,while under Kira's control,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,just prior to their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this information\Nhas been made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take as long as you want\Nto look them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me know what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Come on, this is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a print number\Non the back of each of these photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ignore this fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and was still able\Nto come up with the phrase:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"L, do you know, gods of death\Nlove apples",
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what would that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, if I read it the way Kira\Nintended on my first attempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd only look more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact I'm able\Nto solve this silly code,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't enough on its own\Nto prove that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be quite amazing to learn\Nthat not only could Kira kill others,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but could also control\Nhis victims actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Kira wrote these,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems he's encoded\Na message for you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as if he's mocking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you line these notes up\Nside by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a look\Nat the first letter of every line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it reveals a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rearranging it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,gives you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"L, do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods of Death love apples?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But there're obvious print numbers\Non the back of all these photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrange it in that order, we get:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"L, do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Love apples, Gods of Death "
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.44,0:10:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] That doesn't sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And based on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to believe that Kira\Nwould've wanted you to read it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] That's incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is\Nthere were actually four photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When we add this one, it reads...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"L, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods of Death\Nwho love apples have red hands."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I never made any criminal\Nwrite the letter in this fourth picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing as I only had\Nthree photographs to work with,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,my deduction was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] No, it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, there were four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd figured that out,\Nit would have been perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you knew\Nthe message was incomplete,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you decided that\Nthere were only three notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You never even considered\Nthat there might be a fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What to make of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't just about gauging\Nmy deductive reasoning skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to see\Nwhat my reaction would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep falling for his tricks,\NI'll be playing right into his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you got me there.\NI didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood this message\Nwill lead you to Kira is not very great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we all know\NGods of Death don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were me,\Nfaced with someone who might be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how would you go about establishing\Nthis person's innocence or guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be absolutely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably try\Nto get him to say something
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that was never made public in any way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that only Kira could know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda like what you were doing just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is that I've asked countless detectives\Nthat same question
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and it took most of them minutes\Nto even come up with an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you immediately thought of a scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in which Kira is speaking\Ndirectly to the investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a fine detective, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a bit of double-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The more impressive my answers,\Nthe more of a suspect I become.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, it's about three percent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's made me\Nthat much more determined
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to work with you on this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm in a position\Nwhere even if you are Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it would still be to my benefit\Nto have you working alongside us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I'd say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cooperate with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance I can\Nhelp the investigation to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I'm Kira, I might reveal myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, whether I am Kira or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you stand to gain either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a very smart move on your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think you might be\Ngetting the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I do have\Nan interest in the Kira case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and yes, detective work\Nis a hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that I'm not Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I certainly\Ndon't want to be killed by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what proof\Nhave you been able to give me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you yourself aren't Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it hardly seems fair
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for just one of to be investigated,\Nwouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, neither of us\Ncan prove that we're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you are in fact L,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't imagine it would be that hard\Nfor you to prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,if, say, my father or someone else\Nfrom the task force headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was able to confirm your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do that, then I'm afraid\NI just won't be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure talk a lot, don't you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Typical for someone who hates losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's seven percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it really be him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying you couldn't meet\Nanyone from task force headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to verify my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently working\Nalongside your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as several other\Nsenior detectives from the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if I understand you correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and I take you\Nto task force headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll help us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I safe in making this assumption?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Does this guy have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. What's he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone buzzing]\N-Oh, there goes mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Ryuzaki, I have some bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] Light, your father has--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, it's your--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ambulance siren wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] Okay, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have them call home\Nif you need me to bring anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Light, you take care of him, okay?\N-[Light] Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the doctors think\Nstress was the only cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I thought it was Kira,\Nwhen I first collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've been pushing myself\Na bit too hard lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have added to your stress
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that Light\Nis a suspect in this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually told my father that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in fact, I've told him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true he even knows that I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect his identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we on the task force\Nrefer to him as Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But make no mistake, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is the real L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My father wouldn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The very same man who has been\Ncontrolling the police up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get rid of him\Nand the rest of the investigative team...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's face it.\NIt wouldn't be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have time to sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Light Yagami\Nwho's worried for his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ryuzaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,now that you've had the chance\Nto talk to my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is he cleared as a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say I suspect him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you should know it's very minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve gone over this\Nbut I'll explain it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, Kira killed 12 FBI agents
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd come to Japan to assist us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They were instructed to follow people\Nconnected to the Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these agents, Raye Penber,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,exhibited unusual behavior\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was one of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Raye Penber was investigating\Nbefore he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It only make sense I'd be a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, to be more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one else you could suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I find Light's deductive powers\Nquite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always quick and to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuga, I'd like to help\Nwith the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My father has erased any doubts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have had\Nregarding your true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'd like nothing more\Nthan to catch Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can prove once and for all\Nthat I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a time in your life\Nwhen you should be studying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be too late to join us\Nonce you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how many years that'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, don't you remember my promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That if something ever happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd find Kira and make sure\Nhe gets executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe that my son\Ncould turn out to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] This doesn't seem\Nlike an act to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Or if it is, it's too cheesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Light, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira is pure evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all agree on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking of this whole situation\Nin a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is truly evil
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is the power to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And any person who has come\Nto possess this kind of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you use it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,no true happiness\Ncan be obtained like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by killing other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I think you're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kira is just a normal person,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who somehow obtained this awful power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say that he's cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, I'm sorry for all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be back at work\Nas soon as the doctors let me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[nurse] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting hours were over ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it take to get you\Nto believe that I'm not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, isn't there something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you aren't Kira, it won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let things run their course\Nand the truth will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think it feels\Nto be accused of being Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of the worst feelings ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you were to lock me up for a month
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in a place with no TV or any other kind\Nof access to the outside world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep a constant watch over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Would any normal person be willing\Nto go to such extreme measures
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to clear their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything that would\Ndeprive you of basic human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a complete nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for the investigator\Nto take suggestions from his suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient. It will become apparent to us\Nif you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And listening to that conversation\Nbetween you and your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was almost convinced\Nyou might not be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, please,\Ntake good care of Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know agreed\Nto help with the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't think I'll be able to do much\Nuntil my father is healthy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the L I've been fighting\Nthis whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What is his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are you not Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never once felt cursed\Nsince I picked up the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the thought\Nnever even crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happier than I've ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm going to create\Na perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Honestly, I couldn't care less
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you feel cursed or happy\Nto have the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave that sentimental crap\Nto you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,normally, humans who come\Ninto contact with the Shinigami
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,have nothing but misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no intentions\Nof repeating that pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles] Well, I hope\Nyou're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] What is this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me\Nthis is your ideal of a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you people must think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.30,0:20:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that just mentioning Kira's name
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is enough to get us\Nthe ratings we need, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Our program gets the ratings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because we cover stories\Nthat the other stations won't touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If it bleeds, it leads!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What I need
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is a good fricking story.\NNot this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get out there and find me a story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But the police won't talk, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been impossible to get details\Nfrom them lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! I don't pay you to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they won't give you anything,\Nthen get creative!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[knocking on door]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Demegawa, sir, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who is this from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Now, this is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I call a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"A message to the world from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not broadcast these tapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill your company's\Nboard of directors one by one."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't air these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is for real, our ratings\Nare gonna go through the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited I feel like\NI'm having a heart attack here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED